Charlemagne Capital Ltd - 

http://www.charlemagnecapital.com/





                 
            



                Charlemagne Capital is a specialist emerging markets asset manager, entirely independent of any other group, with a team of dedicated investment professionals at its heart.Their sole focus is the management of emerging market assets, with a variety of products designed to meet the needs of their clients with a heavy bias towards equities, though they  also have some exposure to property and bonds. Their equity products include a range of UCITS compliant long-only funds as well as long/short hedge funds. They also run pooled and segregated accounts for their institutional clients. Products may be global, regional or country-specific. In addition, they manage a number of closed-end property funds and have the experience and ability to construct special purpose vehicles to gain exposure to particular emerging market assets.Charlemagne Capital was established in 2000; with shares in the parent company traded on the Alternative Investment Market (AIM) in London since 2006. Charlemagne personnel own approximately 40% of the issued share capital of the company.Charlemagne Capital is a specialist, independent Emerging Markets investment manager.Their sole business is investment management that focus entirely on Emerging Markets and have no ties with businesses that may result in conflicts of interest. They manage investments in three core product ranges: 

Magna Fund range
Specialist Funds
Hedge Funds.Charlemagne Capital has been best known for its expertise in the markets of Emerging Europe and Russia and has a team of investment professionals dedicated to this region.They have a product range that also encompasses Global Emerging Markets, Greater China as well as an Asian hedge fund and aim to continue to expand our product offerings in the Emerging Markets.













