			Company Description 


			Fiera Capital Corp. is an investment management company. The company offers a spectrum of investment strategies across asset classes, styles and capitalization ranges to institutional investors, private wealth clients and retail investors. It provides retail investors with access to its investment m...
		


                Fiera Capital Corp. is an investment management company. The company offers a spectrum of investment strategies across asset classes, styles and capitalization ranges to institutional investors, private wealth clients and retail investors. It provides retail investors with access to its investment management services; manages and acts as investment manager to mutual funds, including commodity pool funds . Fiera Capital was founded on September 1, 2010 and is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.
            




